snippet.title: Dead or Alive Xtreme Beach Volleyball (Xbox longplay)
snippet.description:
This is just a run through of the entire holiday with one character. My capture crashed a couple of times during recording, so there are tiny sections where a few seconds are missing, but they weren't during anything important.

I wasn't sure what I was getting myself into playing this game. The volleyball controls took a while to get used to, but it seems similar to a dating sim. I'm not too familiar with the characters so it took awhile to understand the gifts each girl would like and there was a whole period in the middle of the video were no one seemed to like me.
